Package remodel.expr

Class UnaryExpression

java.lang.Object
remodel.expr.Expression
remodel.expr.OperatorExpression
remodel.expr.UnaryExpression
All Implemented Interfaces:
PriorityCodes, TokenCodes
public class UnaryExpression
extends OperatorExpression
UnaryExpression is a kind of OperatorExpression with a single operand. A UnaryExpression encapsulates the operator, and the single operand.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Anthony J H Simons
